See More

Nylabone Edibles Natural Nubz Chicken Flavor Dog Chew Toy is a natural chew with a delicious flavor that comes from real chicken. These limited ingredient chews are highly digestible, so they’re easy on your pup’s tummy. Natural Nubz are long-lasting and help promote healthy teeth and gums. Each bone-shaped treat has a unique texture with small nubs that help clean your dog’s teeth as he chews. They’re great for dogs of any size, because you can easily break them apart for smaller bites.

Precautions

Please provide plenty of fresh water when giving any chew or treat. Because this is a natural treat, its sizing, color and appearance may vary this is normal. You may also notice a natural scent and oil while your pal chews; this natural oil may stain your furniture, carpeting or other surfaces. To prevent injury and choking hazard, please watch your pet while they enjoy this treat and be sure to choose the appropriate size chew. If this product splinters or develops sharp edges, throw it away immediately for your pet's safety.

Feeding Instructions

For dogs up to 15 lbs, feed one chew per day. For dogs over 15lbs feed one or more chews per day. Be sure your dog has access to plenty of fresh water. Natural color may stain light-colored surfaces. Supervise the use of all edible chews to ensure that your dog does not bite off pieces too large to swallow. These chews are recommended for dogs with all of their permanent teeth (usually around 6 months). Feed as a treat. This product is not intended to be fed as a meal. Best if used within one month after opening product.

About Nylabone Dental Treats

Denta-C to See the Difference

Help reduce the risk of periodontal disease with preventative dental care from Nylabone Advanced Oral Care products. They contain Denta-C, a scientifically proven blend of ingredients that are clinically proven to reduce plaque that harbors bacteria. Help achieve cleaner teeth, reduced plaque and tartar and fresher breath with Advanced Oral Care.

Brushing for Health

Nylabone Advanced Oral Care toothpaste and toothbrushes are specifically designed for dogs and cats. Regular teeth brushing helps decrease the risk of serious issues in dogs and cats and promote your pet's overall health. Angled bristles help clean even those hard-to-reach places while the flavored toothpaste will make cleaning your four-legged family's teeth simple and rewarding.

Treat Your Dog to Fresher Breath

Advanced Oral Care offers dog treats that clean teeth and freshen breath with chlorophyll while giving your pup a nutritious and tasty reward. For a quick and simple way to control tartar, add liquid tartar remover to your pup's water. By starting a regular dental care routine early, you help promote your dog's overall health.

360° Action

Nutri Dent Complete edible dental chews clean teeth while naturally freshening breath and reducing plaque and tartar. The 360° shape is clinically proven to reduce bad breath and tartar buildup better than weekly brushing. Made with no added sugar or salt, plastic, artificial colors or preservatives, these easy-to-digest treats are a great start to getting your pup's oral health on track.

About Nylabone

Since their first chew toy back in 1955, Nylabone has been dedicated to creating the highest-quality toys, unique dental solutions and long-lasting edible chews. Recommended by veterinarians and designed to promote dental hygiene in dogs and enhance overall mental fitness, Nylabone products help solve problems like destructive chewing and separation anxiety. The wide variety of offerings in all shapes and sizes is sure to have your one-of-a-kind pooch's perfect match.
